Ing '''Ambrosia''' metung yang klasing traditional [[fruit salad]].  Atin ayng [[sour cream]], sweetened [[cream|whipped cream]] (or whipped topping), [[pinya]], [[mandarin orange]] at [[buku]].  Deng aliwang klasi atin lang [[sagin]] o kaya [[strawberries]] o [[marshmallow|miniature marshmallows]].

Dakal kaniti king mauling America, at manibat pa kanitang 19 a [[dilanwa]] king [[America]]. 

